snippet.title: The Twisted case of Matthew Taylor Coleman / Solved True Crime
snippet.description:
The Twisted case of Matthew Taylor Coleman / Solved True Crime

We are going to talk about the strange and disturbing occurrence of that Santa Barbara, California, surf instructor Matthew Taylor Coleman, the father of two children, admitted to killing in one of the most horrible and shocking crimes. Shocking is an understatement. This just happened in 2021. Coleman who was 40 yrs old, he was considered a staple of his community, an evangelical Christian who ran a surfing school and tutored Spanish, the kind of person who was known for his compassion for others. But when he was arrested at the U.S.-Mexico border just hours after the bodies of his children were found, another side of him emerged. Coleman completely out of character, surprisingly told an FBI agent he’d recently been “enlightened” by QAnon — the satanic panic that helped fuel the January 6th insurrection on the U.S. Capitol. His children, he said, had “serpent DNA” they’d inherited from his wife, and he was “saving the world from monsters.
